     1	"""Typed synthesis hints from adaptive modal autoencoder introspection.
     2	
     3	The adaptive layer is allowed to point at friction, not to rewrite law.  This
     4	module converts autoencoder introspection evidence into explicit deterministic
     5	compiler/decompiler/frame-logic work items that can be reviewed, tested, and
     6	implemented as normal typed rules.
     7	"""
